Write a program to find whether the given number is even or odd using the if-else statement

SOURCE CODE:

#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
    // Write C code here
    int a;
    scanf("%d",&a);
    if(a%2==0){
    printf("%d is even number",a);
    }
    else
    {
    printf("%d is odd number",a);
    }
    return 0;
}

INPUT:
15


OUTPUT:
15 is odd number
